{
  "video_id": "JqcDzptviFw",
  "title": "The work that makes all other work possible | Ai-jen Poo",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12944.0,
      "end_time": 14967.0,
      "text": "I want to talk to you tonight"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14991.0,
      "end_time": 18227.0,
      "text": "about the work that makes all other work possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19279.0,
      "end_time": 23637.0,
      "text": "about the millions of women who go to work in our homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23662.0,
      "end_time": 25843.0,
      "text": "every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25867.0,
      "end_time": 29648.0,
      "text": "caring for children as nannies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29672.0,
      "end_time": 33142.0,
      "text": "caring for our loved ones with disabilities and our elders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33166.0,
      "end_time": 34754.0,
      "text": "as home care workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35596.0,
      "end_time": 39474.0,
      "text": "maintaining sanity in our homes as cleaners."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39498.0,
      "end_time": 42440.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the work that makes all other work possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43472.0,
      "end_time": 47400.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s mostly done by women, more than 90 percent women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47640.0,
      "end_time": 49259.0,
      "text": "disproportionately women of color."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49719.0,
      "end_time": 55376.0,
      "text": "And the work itself is associated with work that women have historically done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 58602.0,
      "text": "work that&#39;s been made incredibly invisible"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58626.0,
      "end_time": 61220.0,
      "text": "and taken for granted in our culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62228.0,
      "end_time": 66852.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s so fundamental to everything else in our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66876.0,
      "end_time": 71594.0,
      "text": "It makes it possible for all of us to go out and do what we do in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71618.0,
      "end_time": 72936.0,
      "text": "every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72960.0,
      "end_time": 78183.0,
      "text": "knowing that the most precious aspects of our lives are in good hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79239.0,
      "end_time": 81318.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t think about it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85547.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s almost defined by its invisibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86483.0,
      "end_time": 88166.0,
      "text": "You could go into any neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88190.0,
      "end_time": 91362.0,
      "text": "and not know which homes are also workplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91386.0,
      "end_time": 92958.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92982.0,
      "end_time": 95902.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no list or registry."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95926.0,
      "end_time": 97466.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99791.0,
      "end_time": 105774.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s this work that is not even referred to as real work."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105798.0,
      "end_time": 108700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s referred to as \"help.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108681.0,
      "end_time": 111884.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s often seen as unskilled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111909.0,
      "end_time": 113925.0,
      "text": "not seen as professional."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115631.0,
      "end_time": 121357.0,
      "text": "And race has played a profound role in how we value this work in our culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121381.0,
      "end_time": 124809.0,
      "text": "Some of the first domestic workers in the United States were black women"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 124833.0,
      "end_time": 126253.0,
      "text": "who were enslaved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126277.0,
      "end_time": 130370.0,
      "text": "and racial exclusion has shaped their conditions for generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131660.0,
      "end_time": 134555.0,
      "text": "In the 1930s, when Congress was discussing the labor laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134579.0,
      "end_time": 136730.0,
      "text": "that would be a part of the New Deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136754.0,
      "end_time": 139900.0,
      "text": "that would protect all workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139114.0,
      "end_time": 143880.0,
      "text": "Southern members of Congress refused to support those labor laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 143904.0,
      "end_time": 148707.0,
      "text": "if they included protections for domestic workers and farmworkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 149503.0,
      "end_time": 152763.0,
      "text": "That history of racial exclusion"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 152788.0,
      "end_time": 157775.0,
      "text": "and our cultural devaluing of work that&#39;s associated with women"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 157799.0,
      "end_time": 162740.0,
      "text": "now means that millions of women go to work every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 162980.0,
      "end_time": 163781.0,
      "text": "work incredibly hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 163805.0,
      "end_time": 165903.0,
      "text": "and still can&#39;t make ends meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166639.0,
      "end_time": 171519.0,
      "text": "They earn poverty wages without a safety net,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 171543.0,
      "end_time": 177386.0,
      "text": "so that the women that we&#39;re counting on to take care of us and our families"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 177410.0,
      "end_time": 180402.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t take care of their own, doing this work."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 181983.0,
      "end_time": 187233.0,
      "text": "But my work over the last 20 years has been about changing precisely that."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 187257.0,
      "end_time": 191463.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about making these jobs good jobs that you can take pride in"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 191487.0,
      "end_time": 193259.0,
      "text": "and support your family on."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193835.0,
      "end_time": 197471.0,
      "text": "At the National Domestic Workers Alliance, we&#39;ve been working hard in states"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197495.0,
      "end_time": 202559.0,
      "text": "to pass new laws that will protect domestic workers from discrimination"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 202583.0,
      "end_time": 204709.0,
      "text": "and sexual harassment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 204733.0,
      "end_time": 208959.0,
      "text": "that will create days of rest, paid time off, even."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209766.0,
      "end_time": 214206.0,
      "text": "So far, eight states have passed domestic workers bills of rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 215412.0,
      "end_time": 216590.0,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216614.0,
      "end_time": 220317.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 220341.0,
      "end_time": 222135.0,
      "text": "And during the Obama administration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 222159.0,
      "end_time": 226136.0,
      "text": "we were successful in bringing two million home care workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228700.0,
      "text": "under minimum wage and overtime protections"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 228724.0,
      "end_time": 232563.0,
      "text": "for the first time since 1937."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 232587.0,
      "end_time": 236548.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 238317.0,
      "end_time": 243823.0,
      "text": "Most recently, we&#39;ve been really excited to launch a new portable benefits platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 243847.0,
      "end_time": 246507.0,
      "text": "for domestic workers, called \"Alia,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 246531.0,
      "end_time": 250154.0,
      "text": "which allows for domestic workers with multiple clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 250178.0,
      "end_time": 254472.0,
      "text": "to give them access to benefits for the very first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 255554.0,
      "end_time": 259720.0,
      "text": "So really important progress is being made."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 259793.0,
      "end_time": 262233.0,
      "text": "But I would argue tonight"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 262257.0,
      "end_time": 267484.0,
      "text": "that one of the most important things that domestic workers can provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 267508.0,
      "end_time": 270320.0,
      "text": "is actually what they can teach us"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 270570.0,
      "end_time": 272179.0,
      "text": "about humanity itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 272830.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "and about what it will take to create a more humane world for our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 279774.0,
      "end_time": 282533.0,
      "text": "In the face of extreme immorality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 282557.0,
      "end_time": 286516.0,
      "text": "domestic workers can be our moral compass."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 287309.0,
      "end_time": 289227.0,
      "text": "And it makes sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 289251.0,
      "end_time": 292157.0,
      "text": "because what they do is so fundamental"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 292181.0,
      "end_time": 296484.0,
      "text": "to the very basics of human need and humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 297184.0,
      "end_time": 300987.0,
      "text": "They are there when we are born into this world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 301110.0,
      "end_time": 304857.0,
      "text": "they shape who we become in this world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 305611.0,
      "end_time": 310250.0,
      "text": "and they are with us as we prepare to leave this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 311215.0,
      "end_time": 314719.0,
      "text": "And their experiences with families are so varied."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 314744.0,
      "end_time": 317818.0,
      "text": "They have some relationships with the families that they work for"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 317842.0,
      "end_time": 320950.0,
      "text": "that are incredibly positive and mutually supportive"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 320974.0,
      "end_time": 322932.0,
      "text": "and last for years and years."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 322956.0,
      "end_time": 325631.0,
      "text": "And then the opposite also happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 326209.0,
      "end_time": 330905.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve seen cases of sexual violence and assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 330929.0,
      "end_time": 334575.0,
      "text": "of extreme forms of abuse and exploitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 335753.0,
      "end_time": 338483.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen cases of human trafficking."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 339696.0,
      "end_time": 342934.0,
      "text": "Domestic workers live in poor neighborhoods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 342958.0,
      "end_time": 346993.0,
      "text": "and then they go to work in very wealthy ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 348112.0,
      "end_time": 354102.0,
      "text": "They cross cultures and generations and borders and boundaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 354126.0,
      "end_time": 357251.0,
      "text": "and their job, no matter what,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 357275.0,
      "end_time": 360150.0,
      "text": "is to show up and care --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 361872.0,
      "end_time": 367233.0,
      "text": "to nurture, to feed, to clothe, to bathe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 368406.0,
      "end_time": 371907.0,
      "text": "to listen, to encourage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 372908.0,
      "end_time": 374790.0,
      "text": "to ensure safety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 375415.0,
      "end_time": 377212.0,
      "text": "to support dignity ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 378700.0,
      "end_time": 380776.0,
      "text": "to care no matter what."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 382245.0,
      "end_time": 385779.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you a story of a woman I met early on in this work."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 385803.0,
      "end_time": 387135.0,
      "text": "Her name is Lily."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 388309.0,
      "end_time": 391430.0,
      "text": "Lily and her family lived in Jamaica,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 392350.0,
      "end_time": 395791.0,
      "text": "and when she was 15 years old, she was approached by an American couple"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 395815.0,
      "end_time": 398649.0,
      "text": "who were looking for a live-in nanny to come live with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 398673.0,
      "end_time": 399824.0,
      "text": "in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 399848.0,
      "end_time": 401732.0,
      "text": "and help them care for their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 402295.0,
      "end_time": 407422.0,
      "text": "They offered Lily&#39;s family that if she came to work as their nanny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 407446.0,
      "end_time": 411416.0,
      "text": "she would be able to have access to a US education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 411440.0,
      "end_time": 416230.0,
      "text": "and she would have a weekly salary sent home to help her family financially."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 417819.0,
      "end_time": 419756.0,
      "text": "They decided it was a good idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 419780.0,
      "end_time": 422674.0,
      "text": "and decided to take the opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 424184.0,
      "end_time": 426840.0,
      "text": "Lily held up her end of the bargain"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 428125.0,
      "end_time": 430386.0,
      "text": "and helped to raise three children."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 431957.0,
      "end_time": 435580.0,
      "text": "But all communication with her family was severed:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 435604.0,
      "end_time": 438640.0,
      "text": "no letters, no phone calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 438665.0,
      "end_time": 441188.0,
      "text": "She was never allowed to go to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 442160.0,
      "end_time": 444205.0,
      "text": "and she was never paid --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 444229.0,
      "end_time": 446585.0,
      "text": "for 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 447804.0,
      "end_time": 451488.0,
      "text": "One day, she saw an article in a newspaper about another domestic worker"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 451512.0,
      "end_time": 453961.0,
      "text": "with a really similar story to hers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 453985.0,
      "end_time": 456731.0,
      "text": "another case that I was working on at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 456755.0,
      "end_time": 458752.0,
      "text": "and she found a way to reach me."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 459777.0,
      "end_time": 462399.0,
      "text": "She also found a way to reach her brother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 462423.0,
      "end_time": 465174.0,
      "text": "who was living in the United States at the time as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 465198.0,
      "end_time": 468488.0,
      "text": "Between the two of us, we were able to help her escape."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 469525.0,
      "end_time": 472476.0,
      "text": "And she had the help of one of the children."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 473710.0,
      "end_time": 476895.0,
      "text": "One of the children was old enough to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 476919.0,
      "end_time": 481730.0,
      "text": "that the way his nanny was being treated was wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 481980.0,
      "end_time": 484476.0,
      "text": "and he gave her the money that he had been saving through his childhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 484500.0,
      "end_time": 485733.0,
      "text": "to help her escape."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 487304.0,
      "end_time": 489479.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing about this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 492210.0,
      "end_time": 496806.0,
      "text": "She was essentially enslaved for 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 498248.0,
      "end_time": 501548.0,
      "text": "Human trafficking and slavery is a criminal offense."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 502230.0,
      "end_time": 505180.0,
      "text": "And so her lawyers and I asked Lily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 505204.0,
      "end_time": 508985.0,
      "text": "did she want to press criminal charges for what had happened to her."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 509731.0,
      "end_time": 512696.0,
      "text": "And after thinking about what it would mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 512720.0,
      "end_time": 514309.0,
      "text": "she said no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 515222.0,
      "end_time": 519457.0,
      "text": "because she didn&#39;t want the children to be separated from their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 522113.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526562.0,
      "text": "Instead, we filed a civil lawsuit, and we eventually won the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 526586.0,
      "end_time": 530287.0,
      "text": "and her case became a rallying cry for domestic workers everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 530311.0,
      "end_time": 534877.0,
      "text": "She was reunited with her family and went on to have a family of her own."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 535909.0,
      "end_time": 539255.0,
      "text": "But the thing that&#39;s so profound to me about this story"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 539279.0,
      "end_time": 544189.0,
      "text": "is, despite having 15 years stolen from her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 544214.0,
      "end_time": 549998.0,
      "text": "it did not affect the care and compassion that she felt for the children."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 551300.0,
      "end_time": 554259.0,
      "text": "And I see this from domestic workers all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 554283.0,
      "end_time": 556170.0,
      "text": "In the face of indignities"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 556194.0,
      "end_time": 559985.0,
      "text": "and our failure to respect and value this work in our culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 560900.0,
      "end_time": 562299.0,
      "text": "they still show up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 562323.0,
      "end_time": 563776.0,
      "text": "and they care."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 564780.0,
      "end_time": 568369.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re simply too proximate to our shared humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 568393.0,
      "end_time": 571552.0,
      "text": "They know how your toddler likes to be held"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 571576.0,
      "end_time": 573980.0,
      "text": "as they take their bottle before a nap."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 575110.0,
      "end_time": 577781.0,
      "text": "They know how your mother likes her tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 577805.0,
      "end_time": 581876.0,
      "text": "how to make her smile and tell stories despite her dementia."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 582924.0,
      "end_time": 586640.0,
      "text": "They are so proximate to our humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 587688.0,
      "end_time": 589839.0,
      "text": "They know that at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 589863.0,
      "end_time": 592967.0,
      "text": "these are people who are part of families --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 592991.0,
      "end_time": 594852.0,
      "text": "someone&#39;s mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 594876.0,
      "end_time": 597127.0,
      "text": "someone&#39;s grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 597151.0,
      "end_time": 599601.0,
      "text": "someone&#39;s best friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 599625.0,
      "end_time": 601765.0,
      "text": "and someone&#39;s baby;"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 603773.0,
      "end_time": 605878.0,
      "text": "undeniably human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 606656.0,
      "end_time": 609747.0,
      "text": "and therefore, not disposable."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 611715.0,
      "end_time": 618236.0,
      "text": "Domestic workers know that any time a single person becomes disposable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 620200.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a slippery slope."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 621284.0,
      "end_time": 625238.0,
      "text": "You see, the cultural devaluing of domestic work"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 625262.0,
      "end_time": 629238.0,
      "text": "is a reflection of a hierarchy of human value"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 629262.0,
      "end_time": 631674.0,
      "text": "that defines everything in our world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 632549.0,
      "end_time": 636465.0,
      "text": "a hierarchy that values the lives and contributions"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 636489.0,
      "end_time": 639683.0,
      "text": "of some groups of people over others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 640714.0,
      "end_time": 644292.0,
      "text": "based on race, gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 644316.0,
      "end_time": 647949.0,
      "text": "class, immigration status --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 647973.0,
      "end_time": 650212.0,
      "text": "any number of categories."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 651514.0,
      "end_time": 658198.0,
      "text": "And that hierarchy of human value requires stories about those groups of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 658222.0,
      "end_time": 660915.0,
      "text": "in order to sustain itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 660939.0,
      "end_time": 664500.0,
      "text": "So these stories have seeped deep into our culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 664740.0,
      "end_time": 668454.0,
      "text": "about how some people are less intelligent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 668479.0,
      "end_time": 671716.0,
      "text": "some people are less intuitive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 673810.0,
      "end_time": 674901.0,
      "text": "weaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 674925.0,
      "end_time": 678737.0,
      "text": "by extension, less trustworthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 679371.0,
      "end_time": 680739.0,
      "text": "less valuable"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 681652.0,
      "end_time": 683441.0,
      "text": "and ultimately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 683465.0,
      "end_time": 685100.0,
      "text": "less human."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 686448.0,
      "end_time": 690665.0,
      "text": "And domestic workers know it&#39;s a slippery slope"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 690689.0,
      "end_time": 697339.0,
      "text": "when we start to see a worker as less than a real worker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 698318.0,
      "end_time": 701644.0,
      "text": "to a woman as less than a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 702367.0,
      "end_time": 706277.0,
      "text": "to a mother as less than a mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 707365.0,
      "end_time": 710750.0,
      "text": "to a child as less than a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 712519.0,
      "end_time": 714119.0,
      "text": "In the spring of 2018,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 714143.0,
      "end_time": 718837.0,
      "text": "the Trump administration announced a new policy at the US-Mexico border,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 718861.0,
      "end_time": 721297.0,
      "text": "a zero-tolerance policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 721321.0,
      "end_time": 726162.0,
      "text": "to forcibly separate all children from their parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 726186.0,
      "end_time": 729439.0,
      "text": "who were arriving at the border seeking asylum;"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 729463.0,
      "end_time": 733496.0,
      "text": "children as young as 18 months, separated from their parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 733520.0,
      "end_time": 738608.0,
      "text": "after a long and arduous journey to reach the US-Mexico border"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 738632.0,
      "end_time": 741536.0,
      "text": "in search of safety and a new beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 742542.0,
      "end_time": 745170.0,
      "text": "Thousands of children separated."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 746765.0,
      "end_time": 749545.0,
      "text": "And because they were migrants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 749569.0,
      "end_time": 753400.0,
      "text": "they were treated as less than children."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 755446.0,
      "end_time": 759943.0,
      "text": "In response, I helped to organize the Families Belong Together Vigil"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 759967.0,
      "end_time": 764216.0,
      "text": "at the Ursula Border Patrol Processing Center in McAllen, Texas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 764240.0,
      "end_time": 765478.0,
      "text": "on Father&#39;s Day."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 766650.0,
      "end_time": 769359.0,
      "text": "Inside that processing center, there were hundreds of children"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 769383.0,
      "end_time": 772111.0,
      "text": "who were being held, processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 772135.0,
      "end_time": 775335.0,
      "text": "and then prepared to be shipped all over country"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 775359.0,
      "end_time": 780547.0,
      "text": "to be jailed in facilities hundreds of miles away from their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 781522.0,
      "end_time": 783683.0,
      "text": "I saw with my own eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 783707.0,
      "end_time": 786575.0,
      "text": "children not [old] enough for kindergarten"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 786599.0,
      "end_time": 788840.0,
      "text": "in unmarked buses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 788108.0,
      "end_time": 792372.0,
      "text": "being shipped off to jails hundreds of miles away."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 793904.0,
      "end_time": 796587.0,
      "text": "And as they passed us by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 796611.0,
      "end_time": 799890.0,
      "text": "they reached for us through the windows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 801485.0,
      "end_time": 805333.0,
      "text": "as we stood vigil to let them know that they are not alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 805357.0,
      "end_time": 807100.0,
      "text": "and we are fighting for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 807906.0,
      "end_time": 812237.0,
      "text": "Domestic workers came from all over Texas to be a part of the vigil."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 812261.0,
      "end_time": 816827.0,
      "text": "They saw in those families their own family stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 816851.0,
      "end_time": 822646.0,
      "text": "They had also come here in search of safety and a new beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 822670.0,
      "end_time": 824246.0,
      "text": "a better life for their families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 824270.0,
      "end_time": 827939.0,
      "text": "and they saw in the eyes of those children"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 827963.0,
      "end_time": 829514.0,
      "text": "their own children."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 831520.0,
      "end_time": 832872.0,
      "text": "And through our tears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 833650.0,
      "end_time": 836526.0,
      "text": "we looked at each other and we asked each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 836551.0,
      "end_time": 838621.0,
      "text": "\"How did we get here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 839732.0,
      "end_time": 842526.0,
      "text": "to putting children in cages"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 842550.0,
      "end_time": 846476.0,
      "text": "and separating them from the people who love them the most in the world?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 847159.0,
      "end_time": 848569.0,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 850171.0,
      "end_time": 856104.0,
      "text": "And what I thought to myself was: if domestic workers were in charge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 856128.0,
      "end_time": 857932.0,
      "text": "this never would have happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 858916.0,
      "end_time": 863846.0,
      "text": "Our humanity would never have been so disposable"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 863870.0,
      "end_time": 866543.0,
      "text": "that we would be treating children in this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 869304.0,
      "end_time": 875840.0,
      "text": "The Dalai Lama once said that love and compassion are necessities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 875877.0,
      "end_time": 877525.0,
      "text": "not luxuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 878597.0,
      "end_time": 882237.0,
      "text": "Without them, humanity cannot survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 884341.0,
      "end_time": 888104.0,
      "text": "In other words, they are fundamental to human existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 889644.0,
      "end_time": 894639.0,
      "text": "Domestic workers are in charge of the fundamentals."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 895980.0,
      "end_time": 897992.0,
      "text": "They love and they care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 898160.0,
      "end_time": 900992.0,
      "text": "and they show compassion no matter what."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 904160.0,
      "end_time": 908440.0,
      "text": "We live in a time of moral choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 909417.0,
      "end_time": 911770.0,
      "text": "everywhere we turn:"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 911101.0,
      "end_time": 912755.0,
      "text": "at the border,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 912779.0,
      "end_time": 914999.0,
      "text": "at the ballot box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 915230.0,
      "end_time": 916898.0,
      "text": "in our workplaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 917930.0,
      "end_time": 921473.0,
      "text": "right in our homes, full of moral choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 923267.0,
      "end_time": 929273.0,
      "text": "As you go about your day and you encounter these moral choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 929297.0,
      "end_time": 930799.0,
      "text": "think of Lily."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 932323.0,
      "end_time": 933948.0,
      "text": "Think like Lily."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 935830.0,
      "end_time": 941530.0,
      "text": "Think like a domestic worker who shows up and cares no matter what."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 942228.0,
      "end_time": 945161.0,
      "text": "Love and compassion, no matter what."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 946461.0,
      "end_time": 948839.0,
      "text": "Show up like a domestic worker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 951164.0,
      "end_time": 953792.0,
      "text": "because our children are counting on us."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 954537.0,
      "end_time": 955708.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 955732.0,
      "end_time": 959362.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}